overview:
East liberty medical clinic provides walk in clinic services in the Toronto area.

Unique to East Liberty Medical Clinic is the strong multidisciplinary culture available to you. We offer a complete collaborative experience with physicians, naturopaths, chiropractors, physiotherapists, massage therapists, acupuncturists, gastroenterologists, psychotherapists, sports medicine physicians, medical lab technicians and cardiologists working together. We offer both preventative and therapeutic modalities to ensure total body wellness. All of these services work together in harmony to provide you with the most complete and best possible care in one setting. We also have a in-house medical lab for your convenience.
